{"tid":133724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅登指香港政府收入為800億港元    可見已淪為CONTENT FARM","createTime":"2017-02-25T00:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T04:16:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2f8aca99dfba8ec11741435605489e1bc209fd","tid":133724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T00:46:52.000Z","msg":"先欣賞一下紅燈方面既智障：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s17.postimg.org/a2bfdfazj/800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs17.postimg.org%2Fa2bfdfazj%2F800.jpg&h=c020b639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先姑勿論深圳既數據有多少吹水成份<br />\n香港政府收入點會得800億? 單係賣地都唔止啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">FACT CHECK:</span><br />\n2015-16年度稅局的整體稅收為港幣2,913億元<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/abo/rev.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fabo%2Frev.htm&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTecpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=165e9efe\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/abo/rev.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2015/16年度政府總收入為4500億元<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gov.hk/tc/about/abouthk/factsheets/docs/public_finance.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fabouthk%2Ffactsheets%2Fdocs%2Fpublic_finance.pdf&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTecpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3f09b422\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.hk/tc/about/abouthk/factsheets/docs/public_finance.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"c6e9fbab5bba2fa20827b2e82945646dcf7b69ed","tid":133724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T00:59:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">FACT CHECK</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人口730萬人, 其中100萬為支那單程證殖民, 食綜援既殘人<br />\n再減除老幼, 香港既工作人口約為300萬<br />\n<br />\n支那深圳2015年人口 1137.87萬人<br />\n呢D所謂常住人口, 有大量由外省進入深圳打工既人<br />\n根本近8成深圳人口係實際工作人口黎<br />\n<br />\n[url]http://210.6.198.17/cache/<a href=\"http://www.sztj.gov.cn/xxgk/tjsj/tjnj/201701/W020170120506125327799.pdf?ich_args=69aa18113c80b024a32889be988441ff_1_0_0