dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:35:06.000Z","msg":"香港稅制比支那 低一半以上<br />\n而且香港每年都會出各優惠回贈比人"},{"pid":"b0b21d8ed8837defbc217ed20bb80636106d02c0","tid":133724,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:38:43.000Z","msg":"支那五毛狗就係想唱衰香港<br />\n等香港人唔知自己既重要性"},{"pid":"986e59448dd8e91baeffabc529532aba31971a83","tid":133724,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n2015/16年度政府總收入為4500億元<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gov.hk/tc/about/abouthk/factsheets/docs/public_finance.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fabouthk%2Ffactsheets%2Fdocs%2Fpublic_finance.pdf&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTecpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3f09b422\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.hk/tc/about/abouthk/factsheets/docs/public_finance.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單講利得稅<br />\n支那33%，HK17.5%<br />\nHK收33%的話，收入會點呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那做過生意都知，佢稅制好巧立名目，基本賺1億，有d行業差不多要比50m稅<br />\n<br />\nHK年年退稅，支那？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4192de78c1a1efb42d51c05c56d63cfe8e6c3fe","tid":133724,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:40:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"9796a9f6d752b6774a58c4b3a8d0c6606dee0a3e","tid":133724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五毛黎姐 <br />\n<br />\n班五毛咪撚走過黎就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到青山派同五毛玩泥沙<br />\n<br />\n真係笑而不語<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ff22e9facaafa7f3dc54c9acc987808aff2498","tid":133724,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n2015/16年度政府總收入為4500億元<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gov.hk/tc/about/abouthk/factsheets/docs/public_finance.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fabouthk%2Ffactsheets%2Fdocs%2Fpublic_finance.pdf&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTecpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3f09b422\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.hk/tc/about/abouthk/factsheets/docs/public_finance.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單講利得稅<br />\n支那33%，HK17.5%<br />\nHK收33%的話，收入會點呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那做過生意都知，佢稅制好巧立名目，基本賺1億，有d行業差不多要比50m稅<br />\n<br />\nHK年年退稅，支那？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係有2個老闆<br />\nHK 每月收益100萬<br />\n深圳 每月收益70萬咁<br />\n<br />\nHK就好老闆來,出雙倍人工,唔會欺壓員工,仲成日派獎金咁,賺100萬,但純利就得50萬<br />\n<br />\n深圳就仆街老闆來,低人工,創好多罰$制度,賺70萬,但純利就有60萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後深圳呢個老闆,就不斷話自己勁過HK"},{"pid":"7fba363a84eb43ccc85c1ea8521e0dd7320e01ac","tid":133724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果邊仲有「人」睇?<br />\n<br />\n你唔理下鄉土仲有冇「人」睇?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nfriend forward比我先知呢單野<br />\n<br />\n紅燈根本就變左做垃圾堆填區"},{"pid":"1cd72298e51f38598b1f809182128884ef6818f5","tid":133724,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491ee3dc64ab55d192b216f47983639be9342add","tid":133724,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>果邊仲有「人」睇?<br />\n<br />\n你唔理下鄉土仲有冇「人」睇?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nfriend forward比我先知呢單野<br />\n<br />\n紅燈根本就變左做垃圾堆填區</blockquote><br />\n其實呢個POST,呢度都有